description: The Living World Pet Tunnel for small animals is specially designed to attach to the Living World Tent for small pets and other Living World Tunnels (all sold separately). It provides small animals with extended space for play and exploration. It can also be used as stand-alone play area for tunneling and burrowing. The polyester fabric is easy to clean and makes a crinkly sound for added amusement when your pet moves through it. The tunnel is suitable for indoor or outdoor use and it includes corner ties to secure to the ground. The large size is suitable for rabbits, guinea pigs, and ferrets.

Living World has created a wide variety of pet supplies that are perfect for your small animal. Some of the other small animal supplies include small animal cage accessories including small animal toys, small animal harnesses, small animal carriers, small animal litter box, small animal hammocks, small animal beds, hamster toys, hamster ball, hamster wheel, rabbit toys, rabbit food, rabbit litter box, small animal bedding, guinea pig bedding, hamster bedding, hamster hideouts, guinea pig toys, guinea pig hideouts, guinea pig beds, ferret toys, ferret beds, ferret hammock, chinchilla toys, chinchilla wheel, rabbit toys, rabbit litter box and more (all sold separately)! Living World has also developed a line of small animal cages to help you create the perfect small animal habitat for your furry friend! Some of the small animal enclosures include guinea pig cage, hamster cage, ferret cage, chinchilla cage, rabbit cages, rabbit hutches and more.
